posting_body: ['10710 17th Avenue South, Tacoma, WA 98444', 'Sienna Apartments in Tacoma, WASienna Apartments is a peaceful, secluded apartment community in Tacoma with easy access to shopping, restaurants, Highway 512, I-5, military bases, and several major employers.', 'All this plus just a 4-minute drive to Pacific Lutheran University.', 'Residents at Sienna Apartments gain access to our fantastic community amenities such as a state-of-the-art fitness center, beautiful swimming pool, and updated clubhouse.', 'Have you been looking for a home that is convenient and comfortable at an affordable price?', "Look no further you'll find this and much more at Sienna Apartments.", 'Apartment Features:', 'Patio/Balcony', 'Full Size Washer & Dryer', 'Cable Ready', 'Window Coverings', 'Wood Burning Fireplace', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Community Features:', 'Flexible Monthly Payments with Flex Rent', 'Wireless Internet Access in Clubhouse', 'Parcel Lockers with 24-Hour Access', 'Outdoor Swimming Pool', 'Security Patrol', 'Fitness Center', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
